         <img src="images/about_hotel.jpg" />
        </div>
       </td>
       <td width="394" valign="top" align="left">
        <div style="padding:0px 10px 5px 14px; margin:0">
         <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background-color:#FFF; padding-left:20px;">
          <tbody>
           <tr>
            <td>
             <p style="color:#000; font-size:15px; font-family:'Trebuchet MS', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight:normal; text-align:justify; width:650px; line-height:25px">
              Europ Impex Uk Ltd was started by two young businessmen 

with passion for scrap metal recycling and trade in 2007. They 

have a combined experience in scrap metal trade and export 

of 15 years. The main focus of the business was to provide 

good quality UK scrap metals ( Ferrous and Non Ferrous) to 

South East Asia. Over the years we have built good relations 

and partnerships with Uk Scrap Yards for supply of Quality 

scrap metal and have provided access to export market for 

Uk Scrap yards.
              <br />
              <br />
              In 2014 , we decided to enter into Manufacture and add value 

to scrap metal recycling by entering into a joint venture with 

Panama Alloys India Ltd. based in Ludhiana, Punjab, India. 

Panama Alloys India Ltd. ( PAI) is large group with 

manufacturing Units for making Steel Billets, Steel Rounds 

and Foundry ( Forging Unit). PAI ltd India manufacture both 

Ferrous and Non Ferrous ( AL) products for various industries 

in India.
              <br />
              <br />
              A New Company was formed after the joint Venture with the 

main purpose of supplying scrap to our own company ( PAI 

Ltd India) and to other Industries in Asia. REDDY PAI METALS 

LTD was formed in 2014 with offices in Cardiff and 

Ludhiana, India. Mr Hanish Gupta of Panama Alloys India Ltd. 

joined the board of Directors of REDDY PAI METALS 

LTD.
             </p>
            </td>
           </tr>
          </tbody>
